# Debugging

- When debugging, add a comment **before** the function you are changing: `# AGENT {NAME} DEBUGGING`, and remove it when done.
- `{NAME}` is the name of the chat/session you are operating in.
- This helps avoid conflicting changes when multiple agents work on the codebase at once.
